    "It highlights the interconnected nature of key drivers and barriers to DT adoption within the building industry.",
    "It provides a visual validation of the analytical analysis presented, showing clusters that represent critical areas of focus such as integration, sustainability, and collaboration, which are essential for understanding the motivation behind DT adoption and the complexities involved in its implementation.",
    "This section presents the research findings and descriptive analysis, as well as the categorization of the drivers and barriers to DT adoption in building construction identified through content analysis.",
    "Also, it introduces the idea of MIC as a way to overcome those barriers.",
